{"title":"2021-02-21 平床","virttualPath":null,"html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-2021-02-21-平床\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2021-02-21-%E5%B9%B3%E5%BA%8A\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>2021-02-21 平床</h1>\n<p>前から見に行きたかった平床という廃墟村に行ってきた。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/NwuJSWzeMgQN91ES6\" rel=\"nofollow\">この辺り</a></p>\n<p>入口に地蔵。 Wayfarer 魂が疼く。</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2021-02-21/20210221-134806-P_20210221_134806_1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2021-02-21/20210221-134806-P_20210221_134806_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>村は廃墟だけど、猟友会が拠点にしてる(ように見える)</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"2021-02-21/20210221-135808-P_20210221_135808.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2021-02-21/20210221-135808-P_20210221_135808.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2021-02-21/20210221-135811-P_20210221_135811.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2021-02-21/20210221-135811-P_20210221_135811.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>ここで田んぼつくってるんだ。</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2021-02-21/20210221-140543-P_20210221_140542.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2021-02-21/20210221-140543-P_20210221_140542.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>壊れたトラックにミニユンボ</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2021-02-21/20210221-143830-IMG_20210221_143830.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2021-02-21/20210221-143830-IMG_20210221_143830.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>これ、何かなーと思ったら…</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2021-02-21/20210221-143330-ricoh360.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2021-02-21/20210221-143330-ricoh360.jpg\" alt=\"myimage://2021/2021-02-21/20210221-143330-ricoh360.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>NRG Systems という太陽光？か自然エネルギーの観測機っぽい</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2021-02-21/20210221-143340-IMG_20210221_143341.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2021-02-21/20210221-143340-IMG_20210221_143341.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>監視中。ほんとかいな。</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2021-02-21/20210221-145635-P_20210221_145634.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2021-02-21/20210221-145635-P_20210221_145634.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>この地区で見つけた地蔵は二つ。国土地理院の地図に記載された神社は更地になって、田んぼになっていたようだ。</p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"随筆","updated":"2021-03-01T00:26:56","published":"2021-02-26T00:09:39"}